{"tid":2378379,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今日之後唔好再講周同學悼念會件事","createTime":"2021-01-24T12:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T17:46:53.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7771599b7e631277a95f18646e47147fe2e50da9","tid":2378379,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:04:45.000Z","msg":"科大男生周梓樂2019年11月4日凌晨於將軍澳警民衝突期間，在尚德邨停車場墮樓昏迷，留醫5天後不治，終年22歲。科大學生會早前為周同學逝世舉行半年悼念會，豈料遭校方秋後算賬，有學生會幹事被科大學生紀律委員會褫奪使用校園設施的權利半年、強制執行75小時校園服務令，以及留下紀律處分紀錄；學生會會長及內務副會長更被勒令休學一個學期。學生會對裁決表示極度遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210124/HTPIPCJRK5HKDE5KTNAOEOMBNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2FHTPIPCJRK5HKDE5KTNAOEOMBNI%2F&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCGLrBTEyyW%2B%2F%2BTJtsqEcrWg%3D&h=74b0caf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2FHTPIPCJRK5HKDE5KTNAOEOMBNI%2F&h=b1902be3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210124/HTPIPCJRK5HKDE5KTNAOEOMBNI/</a>"},{"pid":"a3b04e49adb7d8d2d16e789ee1e12a983876f651","tid":2378379,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c887255357514d9be3b51674fce8c1304f87b994","tid":2378379,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T12:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1ac5733634d88b1894ff963a2689c959f0da59","tid":2378379,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}